Package: SimpLin
Type: Package
Title: Simple Linear Regression
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-02-03
Author: Seongwon Im
Maintainer: Seongwon Im <rseongwoni1@gmail.com>
Description: The package runs a simple linear regression analysis. The output includes the estimated coefficients, standard errors, 95% confidence interval for the intercept and slope. The result also includes the predicted values and the residuals.
